    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. The exterior has visible scratches and a few minor dents, and the interior shows noticeable wear including faded upholstery and some scuffs on the trim. The engine runs but has not been recently serviced, and a few minor systems may need attention. Suitable for a buyer willing to accept some cosmetic and minor mechanical imperfections.",
